sec.p:
There was a significant interaction between 
      
       A. marina
       exclusion and detrital enrichment for microalgal biomass (
      
       Table 3
      ; 
      
       Fig. 5
      ). Lugworm exclusion had a negative effect on microalgal biomass in the non-enriched plots (SNK test: 0: A+>A−). In the lugworm-excluded sediment, detrital enrichment enhanced microalgal biomass (SNK test: A−: 0<200 = 600). Values were similar to those measured for the A+ control plots (treatments 200 and 600 in 
      
       Fig. 5
      ).
